##############################################################
The examples corresponds to some of the standard uses of the theory 
implemented in SaX.

As the examples are build to run in few minutes, the calculations are
not at convergence.

It is strongly recommended after the installation of the package to 
run the examples and compare the results with

ATENTION!!!!! EXAMPLE2 and EXAMPLE4 may take some hours
############################################################## 

##############################################################
# to run examples
##############################################################

Some environment variables have to be set

see the file set_env
on the section set pwscf path to binaries
change the DFT_BIN variable

source set_env

go to the directory of the example to run

./jrun

to run all the examples
execute at the examples directory ./jrun_all_examples

##############################################################
